item.title: Bladestroller Quotes
item.description: In late 2002 Peter da Silva changed his Usenet signature to a parody of Blade Runner called Bladestroller: I've seen things you people can't imagine. Chimneysweeps on fire over the roofs of London. I've watched kite-strings glitter in the sun at Hyde Park Gate. All these things will be lost in time, like chalk-paintings in the rain. '-_-' Time for your nap. | Peter da Silva | Har du kramat din varg, idag?
